### Streaming Service — REST Client test file
### Requires VS Code extension: REST Client (humao.rest-client)
###
### Prerequisites:
###   1. cd infra && docker compose up -d postgres redis minio rabbitmq
###   2. nx run streaming-service:migrate
###   3. nx run streaming-service:serve
###
### Auth: service trusts X-User-Id / X-User-Role set by gateway — no JWT needed here
### Note: trackId must exist in track_cache (seeded by Catalog events) before streaming

@baseUrl    = http://localhost:8084
@userId     = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@userId2    = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
@trackId    = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010

# Set after [7] Start session
@sessionId = REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID

###
### ─── HEALTH ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [1] Health check — expects 200 with postgres/redis/minio status
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###
### ─── AUDIO STREAMING ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [2] Stream full file — default bitrate (320), expects 200 or 206
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stream/{{trackId}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

### [3] Stream with explicit bitrate — expects 200 or 206
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stream/{{trackId}}?bitrate=128
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

### [4] Stream with Range header — expects 206 Partial Content
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stream/{{trackId}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER
Range: bytes=0-1048575

### [5] Stream — suffix range (last 512 KB), expects 206
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stream/{{trackId}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER
Range: bytes=524288-

### [6] Stream — no auth (expects 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stream/{{trackId}}

### [7] Stream — track not in cache (expects 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stream/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

###
### ─── HLS PLAYLIST ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [8] HLS master playlist — expects 200, Content-Type: application/vnd.apple.mpegurl
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stream/{{trackId}}/hls
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

### [9] HLS — no auth (expects 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stream/{{trackId}}/hls

### [10] HLS — track not found (expects 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stream/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/hls
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

###
### ─── PLAY SESSIONS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [11] Start session — expects 201, body contains session id
# @name startSession
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

{
  "trackId": "{{trackId}}",
  "bitrate": 320,
  "source": "BROWSE"
}

###

### [12] Start session — minimal body (no bitrate/source), expects 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

{
  "trackId": "{{trackId}}"
}

### [13] Start session — no auth (expects 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackId": "{{trackId}}"
}

### [14] Start session — missing trackId (expects 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

{}

###
### ─── HEARTBEAT ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Replace @sessionId above with value from [11] response before running these
###

### [15] Heartbeat at 10s — below threshold, expects 200, completed=false
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions/{{sessionId}}/heartbeat
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

{
  "positionMs": 10000
}

### [16] Heartbeat at 20s
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions/{{sessionId}}/heartbeat
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

{
  "positionMs": 20000
}

### [17] Heartbeat at 32s — crosses 30s threshold, expects 200, completed=true
### Also fires TrackPlayedEvent to RabbitMQ and increments Redis playcount:{trackId}
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions/{{sessionId}}/heartbeat
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

{
  "positionMs": 32000
}

### [18] Heartbeat after completed — idempotent, expects 200, no duplicate event
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions/{{sessionId}}/heartbeat
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

{
  "positionMs": 60000
}

### [19] Heartbeat — no auth (expects 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions/{{sessionId}}/heartbeat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "positionMs": 15000
}

### [20] Heartbeat — wrong user (expects 404, ownership check)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions/{{sessionId}}/heartbeat
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId2}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

{
  "positionMs": 15000
}

### [21] Heartbeat — session not found (expects 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/heartbeat
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

{
  "positionMs": 15000
}

###
### ─── END SESSION ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [22] End session — COMPLETED reason, expects 200, status=ENDED
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions/{{sessionId}}/end
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

{
  "positionMs": 215000,
  "reason": "COMPLETED"
}

### [23] End session — SKIPPED (user pressed next), expects 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions/{{sessionId}}/end
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

{
  "positionMs": 5000,
  "reason": "SKIPPED"
}

### [24] End session — no auth (expects 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions/{{sessionId}}/end
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "positionMs": 215000,
  "reason": "COMPLETED"
}

### [25] End session — wrong user (expects 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions/{{sessionId}}/end
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId2}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

{
  "positionMs": 215000,
  "reason": "COMPLETED"
}

### [26] End session — not found (expects 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/play-sessions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/end
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

{
  "positionMs": 0,
  "reason": "ERROR"
}

###
### ─── PLAY HISTORY ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [27] Play history — first page, expects 200 with items + totalPages
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/history?page=0&size=20
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

### [28] Play history — second page
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/history?page=1&size=10
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

### [29] Play history — size clamped to 100 max (expects 200, not error)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/history?page=0&size=999
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

### [30] Play history — no auth (expects 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/history

###
### ─── RECENTLY PLAYED ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [31] Recently played — unique tracks, expects up to 20 items
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/history/recently-played
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

### [32] Recently played — different user (expects 200, empty or their own data)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/history/recently-played
X-User-Id: {{userId2}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

### [33] Recently played — no auth (expects 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/history/recently-played

###
### ─── LISTENING STATS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [34] Listening stats — expects totalListeningMs, totalTracks, topGenres, topArtists
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/history/stats
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

### [35] Listening stats — user with no history (expects 200 with zeroed counters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/history/stats
X-User-Id: {{userId2}}
X-User-Role: LISTENER

### [36] Listening stats — no auth (expects 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/history/stats
